  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 24a04ab43ec46244e881a610d2970b30, type: 3}
  m_Name: Kael_Quest_4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestInfo
  initialDialog:
  - The time has come, my friend. We can no longer hide in the shadows while the
    Orc King ravages our lands.
  - But you cannot face him blindly. You must first craft The Genesis Core. Its immense
    power is the only thing capable of breaking the ancient seal on his lair.
  - Take the Core and head to the dark cave beside the Whispering Lake. Slay the
    Orc King, and bring me his horn as absolute proof. Finish this, once and for
    all!
  initialDialogClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 36fd0b1a5badc5740991754dd63d1316, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4a7681b179c97884dbfafd1f41dcdfc9, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2700dcdd06d894b41baa3cef1676f39c, type: 3}
  acceptOption: I am ready. I will craft the Core, slay the King, and bring you his
    horn.
  acceptAnswer: May the spirits guide your blade. The fate of our world rests in
    your hands.
  acceptAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: aa13f2bf2574c2040a13a99aa5b4c030, type: 3}
  declineOption: I am not strong enough yet. I need more time to prepare.
  declineAnswer: Gather your strength, but do not delay for too long. The beast grows
    restless.
  declineAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7b02fcca5160da24ba08997ea71b9587, type: 3}
  comebackAfterDecline: Have you finished your preparations? Are you ready to forge
    the Genesis Core and face the tyrant?
  comebackAfterDeclineClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: b60f944f797979349b4829f656a2d985, type: 3}
  comebackInProgress: The seal on the lakeside cave remains unbroken. Have you crafted
    the Genesis Core yet? The Orc King still breathes!
  comebackInProgressClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d06e3c146bb6a5f4a88c7fefbf7a12ca, type: 3}
  comebackCompleted: By the gods... The Orc King's Horn! You have actually done it!
    The nightmare is finally over!
  comebackCompletedClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f56de347d241eac49956843cb0c1e9f2, type: 3}
  finalWords: ou have given us our world back. Your legend will be sung for generations
    to come. Thank you, hero. Go to the gate at the end of the village and return
    to the ground.
  finalWordsClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fcc6b93be3a87c24d9c66bd84869c796, type: 3}
  coinReward: 9999
  rewardItem1: Heaven's Key
  rewardItem2: 
